decisions.label: decl
decisions.explanation: The file contains registration macros and wrapper functions that delegate tiling to external helpers (ElewiseBaseTiling::DoTiling). No explicit loops, tile size calculations, or UB/GM arithmetic are present in the function bodies.
evidence: L78-L80: TilingForLeakyRelu is a static wrapper that creates LeakyReluTiling and calls RunTiling, no tiling math
L58-L76: RunTiling calls eleBaseTiling.DoTiling with different DAG types, but the actual tiling logic is inside ElewiseBaseTiling, not in this file
L82-L92: TilingPrepareForLeakyRelu fetches platform info and writes to compileInfo, no loops or tile calculations
L94: IMPL_OP_OPTILING registration macro, no implementation
L38-L52: SetTilingData sets tiling key and block dim from precomputed baseTiling, no arithmetic
